      "content": "okay, thanks for being professional about it. but i'm curious though—do you think the 'AuthenticVoice' approach will actually work for the long term? some of the engineers are worried that if we don't have that 'standardized' layer you provide, the data will become too messy for actual commercial apps or even large-scale voice assistants. do you see any issues with moving away from your optimization model?",
